features: Large Capacity & Multi Compartments: WANDF insulated lunch bag measures 9.25 x 6 x 9.5 inches.The maximum capacity is 9L, which is spacious enough to fit 20 cans of cola (355ml). Making it the perfect size for easy carrying while still providing ample space to accommodate your entire lunch. You won't have to worry about struggling with a bulky bag or having to leave your favorite snacks behind.

Separate Food Grade EVA Material Bag: WANDF lunch tote comes with an extra clear bag which made of food-grade, 100% recyclable EVA material.This bag is free from plastic, PVC, or BPA.It serves multiple purposes and can be used for storing snacks or food items.The surface of this material is easy to clean and resistant to moisture and dirt.

Superior Material: Our lunch box is made of a special PU material, which is easy to clean and waterproof. The interior lining of this thermal lunch bag is made of aluminum foil material. With 3mm of thermal pearl foam filling, it guarantees long-lasting warmth or coolness for your food and drinks, up to 12 hours. Stay assured that your meals will remain at the desired temperature. Experience the convenience and reliability of this lunch bag while showcasing its unique style.

Convenient and Portable: The insulated lunch box features a convenient handle design, allowing you to effortlessly carry it by hand. Its lightweight nature and compact size make it a perfect companion for various occasions, whether you're going to work, attending classes, or embarking on a short trip. You can easily grab it and go, without any hassle or discomfort.

Versatile Application: Aside from its primary function as a bentgo lunch boxe, this versatile accessory also serves as a practical tote bag or a compact travel bag. It offers multiple uses to cater to your diverse needs. Use it to store your essentials, carry small items during shopping trips, or keep your belongings organized while traveling. It's a multipurpose companion that adapts to different situations and fulfills various demands.
